ActCanadian Security Intelligence Service Act
PrecisAppointment of MICHEL COULOMBE of Ottawa, Ontario, to be Interim Director of the Canadian Security Intelligence Service, to hold office during pleasure for a term of six months or until such time as a new Director of the Canadian Security Intelligence Service is appointed, whichever is earlier, effective May 13, 2013.
